<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmānbhūsuravaṁśavāridhisudhādhāmōṁgganāvallabhaḥ pānāvāravi śēṣadhātriviṣayē koṁḍēṭivāstavyakaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dhīmānya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> rmma satprabhujanī
<lb n="2"/>śiṣṭēṣṭacintāmaṇiḥ kannēnākhyamahātmadharmmaniratō jātāṁbikānaṁddanaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē ṣaḍuradrikhēṁddugaṇitē māsē kuhau phālguṇē kāvyē dē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vagurōdayē guṇanidhissaujanyaratnākaraḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kannēnāma mahāmatirbbalayutō viṣṇupriyō dhārmmikaḥ dadyādbā<unclear>va</unclear>surēśvarāya ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>hatērddīpaṁ sthiraṁ ccāgrataḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrīmatribhuvanacakravartti śrīrājarājadēvara vijayarājya saṁvatsaraṁbulu 9 yagu śrāhi śakavarṣaṁbulu 1076
<lb n="5"/>nēṁṭṭi phālguṇa bavāla paṁccādasiyu śukravāramunāṁḍu sūryyagrahaṇa nimittamuna nuttamacōḍavalanāṁṭṭi <unclear>ka</unclear>mmanāṁṭṭi rājamāṇi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kavuramaina prēṁppalli śrībhāvanārāyaṇadēvaraku pānavāramulōni Agrahāramaina kōnṭēṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṁḍaina ko <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>ju koḍuku kannamarāju Ācaṁdrārkka makhaṁḍavartti dīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina birudumāḍalu va<unclear>ṁḍre</unclear>ṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīniṁ jēkoni Apparāju
<lb n="8"/>koḍuku nallabavvanayu<note n="74-2">The inscription is</note> 
